title: Caley's Courgette Cake
ingredients: ['3 eggs', '400g caster sugar', '225ml vegetable oil', '1 tablespoon vanilla extract', '225g grated courgette', '250g plain flour', '1 1/2 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1/4 teaspoon baking powder', '1 teaspoon salt', '60g chopped walnuts']
